        <h2 id="G">G</h2>
        <h3>GP</h3>
        <p>Where someone may see either a GP or another health professional, for example in a hospital setting, use “doctor”.</p>
        <h3>gullet</h3>
        <p>We use “food pipe”.</p>
        <a class="nhsuk-back-to-top-link nhsuk-u-margin-bottom-8" href="#nhsuk-a-z-list">
