        <h2 id="L">L</h2>
        <h3>licensed for</h3>
        <p>For medicines, we say “can be used for” or is or isn’t “officially approved for”.</p>
        <h3>lifelong</h3>
        <p>One word.</p>
        <h3>lip-reading</h3>
        <p>With a hyphen.</p>
        <a class="nhsuk-back-to-top-link nhsuk-u-margin-bottom-8" href="#nhsuk-a-z-list">
